==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Go-out
<hw>Go"-out`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A sluice in
embankments against the sea, for letting out the land waters, when the
tide is out.</def> <altsp>[Written also <asp>gowt</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

